{
  "texts": [
    "To test the short-cuts in candidate answers, we obtain the edited Question-Answer (QA) and Video-Answer (VA) data by prompting GPT-4, again followed by human checking and correction.",
    "Our specific prompts are listed in Tab. 7.",
    "For human checking, we specifically check the edited negative options to ensure that they are actual wrong answers with regard to the question and video contents.",
    "To obtain questions with spoken prefixes, we first prompt GPT-4 to generate a set of spoken phrases that humans typically use before asking questions as shown in Tab. 4.",
    "Then, we randomly select from these spoken phrases and prepend them to the questions."
  ]
}